This paper is about improving the communication aspects of distributed machine learning systems, which involves managing network transfers and determining communication patterns. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also discusses improving convergence and efficiency, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also mentions fault tolerance, which is a topic related to systems (cs.SY) and data structures (cs.DS).
